data.description: Double, wooded, residential lot in the very nice subdivision of Perdido Estates. A mere 5 minutes from the beautiful beaches of Perdido Key, NAS Pensacola's back gate, shopping centers, and located in a great school district. This is one of a few remaining lots that are for sale in this subdivision. Perdido Estates offers underground utilities, and the lot is in Flood zone area X; Area of minimal flood hazard, usually depicted on FIRMs as above the 500-year flood level. The buyer(s) are to verify lot size and zoning/usage. Build your Dream Home here.
